Michael Jackson, a DJ based in Lagos where hr ran an internet fraud scheme has been busted.
Operatives of the EFCC arrested him on Tuesday
According to the commission’s statement,  EFCC arrested him after credible intelligence on the illegal activities of some individuals allegedly involved in computer-related fraud.
“Jackson, who poses as Ella, a transgender woman, allegedly defrauded unsuspecting victims of millions of Naira,” the EFCC said.
“The suspect, who also claimed to be a Disc Jockey, DJ, had in his possession fetish items, which he claimed was ‘for grace and success’.”
Fraudsters operating the advanced fee criminalities have been desperate lately the way they deploy voodoo tactics to capture their victims.
